{"tid":340221,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[模型友請入] 添置噴筆加泵問題","createTime":"2017-07-29T17:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T09:53:34.000Z","uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec53957f77ce55632447e1f039c83809bece540","tid":340221,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"細佬啱啱跌入左模型呢個深坑，但玩左排發現噴罐唔太夠做，d色唔夠勻。<br />\n想借問各位巴打/巴絲平時用開咩噴筆同泵？<br />\n有冇平價又好用既噴筆同泵推介？<br />\n有圖歡迎share，作品圖亦可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本人盡量唔想用國產淘寶噴筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求各位相助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def2fccb3ad2a7870183886b76dc61f28af29605","tid":340221,"uid":60470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"都係新手，剛玩噴油無耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左最cheap果隻230白一口"},{"pid":"e68092b3f9e88bd23da40fa84c49bfb98b2dd962","tid":340221,"uid":60470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係新手，剛玩噴油無耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左最cheap果隻230龜泵連噴筆套裝<br />\n結論係個泵真係唔太掂，又無力出氣又唔穩定，建議比多少少買個好D既泵<br />\n黎緊想換呢隻<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/174155_0294da695dec006960a88fe46738611b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F174155_0294da695dec006960a88fe46738611b.jpg&h=7472e881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n筆就買支大陸垃圾筆先都無妨，最主要可以要黎熟習下拆洗、保養各樣野，買左好筆之後都可以退落黎做下噴底油之類既粗重野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少少心得</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2926ddb91520f838a0367cbe71f6a40247949b1e","tid":340221,"uid":60470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"而家支主筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雙星74537<br />\n香港買應該六百幾